text: Cow head may refer to head of a cow, or a head of cattle. It may also refer to: * Cow Head (town), a town in the Canadian province of Newfoundland and Labrador * Cow Head Group, a geologic group in Newfoundland and Labrador * Cow head protests, which occurred in Selangor, Malaysia in 2009 * Gozu ("Cow Head"), a Japanese urban legend * Gozu, or Yakuza Horror Theatre: Cow's Head, a 2003 Japanese film directed by Takashi Miike * Ox-Head and Horse-Face, characters in Chinese mythology
title: Cow head
